[
  {
    "chunk_id": "mineru_notes_1ba14cb325bc448f7201b20502ecf2b5_100_0",
    "text": "有利于因地制宜进行产业结构的调整.使农林牧副渔全面发展，可以增加农民 收入.促进当地经济发展，改善农民生活条件，提高生活质量：有利于保护土地资源 改善当地的生态环境：有利于促进生态和经济可持续发展.",
    "canon_role": "support_paragraph",
    "bbox": [
      0.11808461180846118,
      0.1539980256663376,
      0.9381682938168294,
      0.24152681803224746
    ],
    "page": "notes_1ba14cb325bc448f7201b20502ecf2b5_100",
    "order": 1
  },
  {
    "chunk_id": "mineru_notes_1ba14cb325bc448f7201b20502ecf2b5_100_1",
    "text": "3.干旱缺木问题",
    "canon_role": "support_paragraph",
    "bbox": [
      0.11901441190144119,
      0.28101349128002634,
      0.29381682938168296,
      0.3027311615663047
    ],
    "page": "notes_1ba14cb325bc448f7201b20502ecf2b5_100",
    "order": 2
  },
  {
    "chunk_id": "mineru_notes_1ba14cb325bc448f7201b20502ecf2b5_100_2",
    "text": "我国典型地区：华北地区、西北、长江中下游地区 产生原因：",
    "canon_role": "support_paragraph",
    "bbox": [
      0.15620641562064155,
      0.3112866074366568,
      0.6387726638772664,
      0.3645936163211583
    ],
    "page": "notes_1ba14cb325bc448f7201b20502ecf2b5_100",
    "order": 3
  },
  {
    "chunk_id": "mineru_notes_1ba14cb325bc448f7201b20502ecf2b5_100_3",
    "text": "(1)自然原因：温带季风气候，全年降水少、河流径流量小；降水变率大；春季蒸 发旺盛。",
    "canon_role": "support_paragraph",
    "bbox": [
      0.11715481171548117,
      0.37314906219151034,
      0.9456066945606695,
      0.42711418229680814
    ],
    "page": "notes_1ba14cb325bc448f7201b20502ecf2b5_100",
    "order": 4
  },
  {
    "chunk_id": "mineru_notes_1ba14cb325bc448f7201b20502ecf2b5_100_4",
    "text": "(2)人为原因：人口稠密，工农业发达，需水量大；木污梁严重；浪费多、利用率低； 春季春种用水量大.",
    "canon_role": "support_paragraph",
    "bbox": [
      0.11622501162250116,
      0.43566962816716026,
      0.9493258949325895,
      0.48963474827245806
    ],
    "page": "notes_1ba14cb325bc448f7201b20502ecf2b5_100",
    "order": 5
  },
  {
    "chunk_id": "mineru_notes_1ba14cb325bc448f7201b20502ecf2b5_100_5",
    "text": "治理措施：南水北调；修建水库：控制人口数量，提高素质：减小水污染：减 少浪费、提高利用率：限制高耗水工业的发展：发展节水农业：采用滴灌、喷灌农业 灌溉技木，提高利用率：实行水价调节，树立节水意识；海水淡化等。",
    "canon_role": "support_paragraph",
    "bbox": [
      0.11808461180846118,
      0.4981901941428101,
      0.9511854951185496,
      0.58571898650872
    ],
    "page": "notes_1ba14cb325bc448f7201b20502ecf2b5_100",
    "order": 6
  },
  {
    "chunk_id": "mineru_notes_1ba14cb325bc448f7201b20502ecf2b5_100_6",
    "text": "4.土壤次生盐碱化",
    "canon_role": "support_paragraph",
    "bbox": [
      0.12273361227336123,
      0.6238894373149062,
      0.34402603440260343,
      0.6456071076011846
    ],
    "page": "notes_1ba14cb325bc448f7201b20502ecf2b5_100",
    "order": 7
  },
  {
    "chunk_id": "mineru_notes_1ba14cb325bc448f7201b20502ecf2b5_100_7",
    "text": "我国典型地区，黄淮海平原、宁夏平原、河套平原等 产生原因：",
    "canon_role": "support_paragraph",
    "bbox": [
      0.14318921431892143,
      0.6508719973675551,
      0.6722454672245467,
      0.7074695623560382
    ],
    "page": "notes_1ba14cb325bc448f7201b20502ecf2b5_100",
    "order": 8
  },
  {
    "chunk_id": "mineru_notes_1ba14cb325bc448f7201b20502ecf2b5_100_8",
    "text": "(1)自然原因：频粱的旱涝气候(黄淮海平原)；地形低洼：大气降水少，以灌溉 水源为主。",
    "canon_role": "support_paragraph",
    "bbox": [
      0.11901441190144119,
      0.7160250082263903,
      0.9483960948396095,
      0.769990128331688
    ],
    "page": "notes_1ba14cb325bc448f7201b20502ecf2b5_100",
    "order": 9
  },
  {
    "chunk_id": "mineru_notes_1ba14cb325bc448f7201b20502ecf2b5_100_9",
    "text": "(2)人为原因：不合理的灌溉：不合理的水利工程建设(渭河平原) 治理措施：",
    "canon_role": "support_paragraph",
    "bbox": [
      0.1701534170153417,
      0.7772293517604475,
      0.8219432821943282,
      0.8331688055281342
    ],
    "page": "notes_1ba14cb325bc448f7201b20502ecf2b5_100",
    "order": 10
  },
  {
    "chunk_id": "mineru_notes_1ba14cb325bc448f7201b20502ecf2b5_100_10",
    "text": "引淡淋荡；井排井灌；生物措施：农田覆盖：合理的灌溉，不能只灌不",
    "canon_role": "support_paragraph",
    "bbox": [
      0.17387261738726173,
      0.8404080289568937,
      0.9493258949325895,
      0.8956893715037841
    ],
    "page": "notes_1ba14cb325bc448f7201b20502ecf2b5_100",
    "order": 11
  },
  {
    "chunk_id": "mineru_notes_1ba14cb325bc448f7201b20502ecf2b5_100_11",
    "text": "排：采取喷灌、滴灌技术等",
    "canon_role": "support_paragraph",
    "bbox": [
      0.1199442119944212,
      0.8719973675551168,
      0.4072524407252441,
